reviews.name: FRAM High Mileage Oil Filter, HM3682
reviews.reviewText: I've been using Fram Filters for more than 20+ years. Never a problem, and love these gripped ends for ease of install and take out. I have a Ford F150 and uses Fram's website to find the filter right for my truck and looked it up on walmart.com.
reviews.title: Fram for life

reviews.name: FRAM High Mileage Oil Filter, HM3682
reviews.reviewText: The price for this product was at least 20% cheaper than the sale price at another store
reviews.title: Motor oil, good price

reviews.name: FRAM High Mileage Oil Filter, HM3682
reviews.reviewText: This filter will perform for 8K miles as it has on my vehicle using synthetic blend. My vehicle has over 150K miles and I have used this filter since it was introduced. A great buy and value.
reviews.title: Good Value,Great Filter

reviews.name: FRAM High Mileage Oil Filter, HM3682
reviews.reviewText: We buy this brand often, and our cars run without issue so i guess they are fine.
reviews.title: i guess i does what its supposed to

reviews.name: FRAM High Mileage Oil Filter, HM3682
reviews.reviewText: I have a 99' Toyota Corolla with close to 150K miles. By using this filter, I can reassure myself that the engine of my Corolla will remain clean, which maintains its responsiveness and helps extending the life of the engine.
reviews.title: Keeping High Mileage Engine Clean
